entiment, but potential doesn't actually mean anything if it's just sitting there."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The only way to actually cash in on that potential is through the quiet, often invisible work of practice. Not the glamorous, montage-worthy practice, but the “I really don't want to do this today” kind of practice."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"space-y-3","children":[["$","h3",null,{"children":"Where Consistency Wins"}],"$L5","$L6","$L7"]}],"$L8"]}]}],"$L9"]}],["$La"],"$Lb"]}],{},null,false,null]},null,false,"$@c"]},null,false,null],"$Ld",false]],"m":"$undefined","G":["$e",["$Lf"]],"S":true,"h":null,"s":"$undefined","l":"$undefined","p":"$undefined","d":"$undefined","b":"rVi7zXwrfZMW6Ulc6UGvq"}
