5:["$","p",null,{"children":"We believe that greatness isn't a lightning bolt. It's a scoreboard."}]
6:["$","p",null,{"children":"That's why we focus on the consistency score. It's not about being a perfect human being 100% of the time (good luck with that). It's about owning your data. It's about seeing the “freak” in yourself.                    "}]
7:["$","p",null,{"children":"We wanted to create a space for the people who care about the rhythm of their week. For the people who know that doing something small every single day is infinitely more powerful than doing something huge once a month."}]
8:["$","section",null,{"className":"space-y-3","children":[["$","h3",null,{"children":"The Freaks"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We're here for the people who are a little too intense about their morning routine. For the ones who track their habits not because they have to, but because they love to show up, every single time. We want to know that when the world got messy, we stayed consistent."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"If you're the type of person who actually enjoys seeing your consistency climb from 70% to 80%, you're in the right place. You aren't “optimizing your life.”                You're shaping the pattern."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"And it adds up. Until one day, it's not effort anymore. It's just you."}]]}]
